routeFacts.name: Sherman Hill
routeFacts.description: Welcome to Wyoming! Experience challenging grades, heavy freight, and iconic motive power in the heart of Union Pacific territory. Conquer the Continental Divide and keep America thriving in Train Sim World 2: Sherman Hill.
routeInfo: Sherman Hill features around 76 miles of track, becoming the longest Train Sim World route at the time of its release. 62 miles are taken up by the mainline from Cheyenne to Laramie, and another 14 miles are added with an extra line between Laramie and Hermosa. Track 3, an extra line that features a less steep grade, is not included with the route. The route runs through the plains of Wyoming, where most of the scenery is grassy fields with the occasional rocks. There are two large freight yards on each end of the route, one at Cheyenne, and one at Laramie. There are a few industries along the route such as the Granite Quarry.
